Package.Definition: XML language for external reporting of SCAP-based network device assessment data.
Package.Comment: For use by Network Vulnerability Scanners and Federal Desktop Core Configuration (FDCC) scanners. Also for use by tools that collect information about devices installed on a network along with configuration information about installed operating systems, applications, settings, vulnerabilities, and open ports.
